summary: Test FC single and multipath device online/offline functionality
description: |
    This test suite validates FC device resilience by:
    1. Single FC device test:
        - Using first available FC device
        - Cycling device offline/online many times
        - Verifying data integrity through FIO
    2. Multipath FC device test:
        - Using first available multipath device
        - Getting all active paths
        - Cycling paths offline/online many times
        - Verifying both path and multipath device data
component:
    - kernel
    - device-mapper-multipath
test: pytest online_offline.py
tag+:
    - multipath
